{"tid":1858972,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一國兩制=香港政府用納稅人嘅錢高價買清市場嘅口罩，再免費送去北京","createTime":"2020-02-03T04:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T04:31:50.000Z","uid":131691,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"71d81b8858e06a30aa0e6b3c486de3d2097a1cd9","tid":1858972,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"印尼嗰邊嘅口罩已經被港共政府一手搶購哂，一啲原本諗住入貨再成本價（或甚至免費）賣俾香港人嘅良心商戶俾政府折斷咗個plan<br />\n<br />\n根本成個口罩危機嘅病根，同6月開始抗爭之前嘅病根一樣：<br />\n<strong>香港淪爲北京嘅白手套</strong><br />\n之前：支那用香港嘅特別經濟地位繞過關稅，繞過經濟制裁，偷盡世界嘅科技<br />\n而家：支那用香港嘅特別經濟地位買清亞洲甚至成個世界嘅口罩，再免費輸出去北京<br />\n<br />\n香港一日唔脫離一國兩制呢個地獄，香港人一日都唔會有好日子過"},{"pid":"054c8b880b508bbb8e49b39678739de9da61ed67","tid":1858972,"uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔反對香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720c3b3237cfae5f703901f9e879d2b96af1d69a","tid":1858972,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"連口罩都要奶共，香港獨立，唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n望下台灣，完全係有主權嘅天堂同垃圾傀儡地獄嘅分別"},{"pid":"eb2477b80ef01fb159d555270cf01ec3991ac153","tid":1858972,"uid":136431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>冇主權乜撚都假</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"cdce4d381367664c6f94ba4fd6a5abd387810f81","tid":1858972,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"依場係奪取主權嘅運動"},{"pid":"9e7cc30f234ddf9e95162cde333dbccc15b53b99","tid":1858972,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fjSk03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t